titleStmt.title: To His Grace, His Majesties High Commissioner, and the Right Honourable the Estates of Parliament. Mr. Allexander Higgins of Craigforth.
titleStmt.author: Higgins, Alexander, of Craigforth, fl. 1695.

notesStmt.note: Proposes that the dispute between Alexander Higgins and John Callander should be referred to the Lords of Justiciary.
Reproduction of the original in the National Library of Scotland.
